          description='Cerro Madsen, 1800msnm, is located on the way to the Laguna de los Tres, on ​​the Fitz Roy range area. Getting to its summit means an adventure of low difficulty dealing with all kinds of terrain; a great option as a first experience in the area. From its summit you can enjoy the majestic views of the surrounding glaciers; with Cerro Fitz Roy standing imposing as a gift to our effort.'
